page.title: 10Dunnington Organisations
page.content:
There are a wide variety of organisations within Dunnington village which appear to cater for the main interests and tastes of this village of 4500 people.
Bridge Club Conservative Club Dunnington Christian Fellowship Dunnington Parish Council Dunnington Players Scouts and Guides (and Supporters) Friday Club Karate Club Mothers and Toddlers Group Parent Teachers Association Playgroup Reading Room Management Committee ST.John's Ambulance Brigade Wives Club Women's Institute Youth Club
